text: Mizanur Rahman Manu is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Dinajpur-4. ==Career== Manu was elected to parliament from Dinajpur-4 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1991 and 1996. He is a former whip of the parliament of Bangladesh. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
